Text: Maksym Yegorychev interview at OwenHarry It was really nice talking to you this week I hope I could provide you with information sufficient for making the right decision From my side I once again want to highlight the fact that if I am given a chance I will do all I can to prove that the people who gave me this chance made the right decision With best regards Maksym Yegorychev MBA OGSM

time to talkHarry I would like to talk to you about the decision Enron made regarding summer internship and how I could improve my chances next time Could you advise me on the time to call you BR Maksym Yegorychev
